item.title: CVE-2019-10396|2024-08-04T22:17:20.506Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20dashboard%20view%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Dashboard View Plugin 2.11 and earlier did not escape build descriptions, resulting in a cross-site scripting vulnerability exploitable by users able to change build descriptions.
